             was indicted for <rs id="t18150510-60-off363" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18150510-60-off363" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150510-60-off363" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18150510-60-cd364" type="crimeDate">29th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150510-60-off363 t18150510-60-cd364"></join>, two silver teaspoons, value 3 s. a child's pelisse, value 15 d. a shift, value 1 s. a gown, value 4 s. a handkerchief, value 1 s. a napkin, value 4 d. a towel, value 4 d. a remnant of linen, value 15 d. and two pillow-cases, value 6 d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               <persName id="t18150510-60-victim616" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
                  Engley
               <interp inst="t18150510-60-victim616" type="surname" value="Engley"></interp>
